Fresh squids cooked adobo style! We love it very much and it really shows – this is the second video of Adobong Pusit
 Preserve the ink duct if you buy the squid fresh or you can always use squid/cuttlefish ink sold in packets. Most supermarkets here in Madrid sell &ldquo;tinta de sepia/calamar&rdquo;
 Cuttlefish ink packet   Cook the squid at high heat in less time until it gets tender and add the vinegar for last.
